1
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:07,800
I heard about the fire at Linglong Pavilion last night.

2
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:11,320
All the servants inside perished in the flames.

3
00:01:11,360 --> 00:01:12,720
The weather is dry.

4
00:01:13,200 --> 00:01:14,930
Accidents are bound to happen.

5
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,440
It's not over yet.

6
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:18,039
Let's put that aside for now.

7
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:22,160
I wonder what brings Princess Tuoya here.

8
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:24,800
Regarding our cooperation proposal last time,

9
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:26,260
have you thought about it?

10
00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:27,920
I still can't accept it.

11
00:01:27,920 --> 00:01:31,080
Standing side by side with someone who hurt the Song Army.

12
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:32,680
You're being too serious, Miss Song.

13
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,000
There are no kin on the battlefield.

14
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,460
Who hasn't raised a blade?

15
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:37,360
If you, Miss Song, because of the past,

16
00:01:37,360 --> 00:01:38,820
want to draw a line with me,

17
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:41,000
why come to listen to me today?

18
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,479
I'm talking to you,

19
00:01:42,479 --> 00:01:44,210
but it doesn't mean I trust you.

20
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:48,080
Whether you trust me or not doesn't matter to me.

21
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:51,680
But I have news you can't afford to miss.

22
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:54,640
Think about it.

23
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,520
What if I told you

24
00:01:57,840 --> 00:02:00,800
I have news about that missing squad of the Song Army?

25
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:04,920
Say that again.

26
00:02:05,160 --> 00:02:07,040
They weren't wiped out.

27
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,840
Some are at Yuelan Mountain.

28
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:13,320
My people found traces of survival there.

29
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:14,920
There were remains of campfires,

30
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:17,850
and fabric scraps from the Song Army's unique flags.

31
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:19,730
Is this information reliable?

32
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,040
If I weren't sure,

33
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,840
how would I dare mention it to you?

34
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:25,160
But the terrain at Yuelan Mountain is complex.

35
00:02:25,160 --> 00:02:26,520
Full of cliffs and ravines.

36
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,680
If one wants to hide people,

37
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:29,520
it's naturally the most convenient place.

38
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:31,760
If you want to confirm it yourself,

39
00:02:32,160 --> 00:02:35,040
it won't be easy.

40
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:42,500
Princess Tuoya, you've told me all this.

41
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,079
What do you want in exchange?

42
00:02:44,079 --> 00:02:45,680
An opportunity.

43
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:48,160
A chance to cooperate again.

44
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:51,520
Then I'm afraid you'll be disappointed.

45
00:02:51,920 --> 00:02:55,160
No matter. Consider it a favor you owe me, Miss Song.

46
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:57,920
Thanks for the news.

47
00:02:58,480 --> 00:03:00,120
If you change your mind, Miss Song,

48
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:01,720
remember to find me anytime.

49
00:03:06,840 --> 00:03:08,200
Yuelan Mountain.

50
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,760
Huanghuacai.

51
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:22,079
For Tuoya to tell you this now,

52
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:24,050
there must be something wrong.

53
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:26,579
No matter what the problem is,

54
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:28,000
I have to go and check.

55
00:03:28,040 --> 00:03:29,770
It's too dangerous to go alone.

56
00:03:30,079 --> 00:03:31,880
Don't worry, I know what I'm doing.

57
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:32,680
I'll go with you.

58
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,560
You can't go.

59
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,600
The Marquis isn't at the residence.

60
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:38,460
Zhongyi Manor can't afford any mistakes right now.

61
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:45,000
Then promise me, no matter what happens,

62
00:03:45,640 --> 00:03:46,770
you must stay alive.

63
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:50,320
Don't worry. No one can kill me.

64
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,040
Huanghuacai.

65
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,760
You must come back safely.

66
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,080
Are you worried about me?

67
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:06,680
Huanghuacai.

68
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,680
I will come back safely.

69
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,460
Then I'll wait for you.

70
00:04:12,720 --> 00:04:13,840
If you don't come back,

71
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:16,079
I'll go to Yuelan Mountain and drag you back.

72
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,519
If you dare to go,

73
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,440
I'll knock you out

74
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:19,480
and carry you home.

75
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,740
That would be worth it.

76
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:43,159
Song Xuan will appear soon.

77
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,440
Are you confident?

78
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,360
Go.

79
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:53,840
Chuyi.

80
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:55,960
Chuyi, wake up!

81
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:57,200
Chuyi.

82
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:13,120
Sleep well, Chuyi.

83
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:15,200
I will definitely protect you.

84
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,840
Shen Lingbo, you lunatic.

85
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,200
You actually dared to kill your father.

86
00:06:26,320 --> 00:06:27,960
Failed treason means death.

87
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,560
Shen Lingbo.

88
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:33,260
Aren't you afraid of retribution for what you've done?

89
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:36,050
I have never believed in retribution.

90
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,600
Speak.

91
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,800
You asked me here.

92
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,890
What do you want me to do now?

93
00:06:48,120 --> 00:06:49,200
What is this?

94
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:50,240
A pill for feigning pregnancy.

95
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,200
A pill for feigning pregnancy.

96
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:54,400
Taking it will make your pulse seem like you're pregnant.

97
00:06:54,800 --> 00:06:56,060
Why should I take this?

98
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:59,159
The Emperor's only remaining healthy son

99
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:00,560
is the Third Prince.

100
00:07:00,960 --> 00:07:01,840
Tell me,

101
00:07:03,960 --> 00:07:05,800
if there were another prince,

102
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,720
how would the situation change?

103
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:11,400
Who would the throne go to then?

104
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:14,220
You want to confuse the royal bloodline.

105
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:17,960
Are kings and nobles born noble?

106
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:21,920
I won't help you do this.

107
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:24,400
Do you think you have a choice?

108
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:28,800
I said I won't help you do this.

109
00:07:32,600 --> 00:07:34,040
Don't test my patience.

110
00:07:44,960 --> 00:07:46,800
Oh, it's been three days.

111
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,920
Why isn't Huanghuacai back yet?

112
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:51,280
Brother, calm down.

113
00:07:51,320 --> 00:07:53,320
Maybe Sister-in-law just got delayed.

114
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,480
Easy for you to say.

115
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:56,400
It's not the Third Prince who's missing.

116
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:58,720
Brother, how can you say that?

117
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:03,280
Third Prince, why are you here?

118
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:05,400
Is Song Xuan missing?

119
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:06,720
Do you know already?

120
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:08,120
The whole court knows.

121
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:10,800
That's not right.

122
00:08:10,880 --> 00:08:13,280
Huanghuacai's operation was very secret.

123
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:15,360
Even if someone knew she was missing,

124
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:17,600
it shouldn't have spread through the court by now.

125
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,120
Instead of worrying about Song Xuan,

126
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,600
you should worry about the Bai family.

127
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,460
The Bai family?

128
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:23,080
What happened to our family?

129
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,400
Didn't Father go to fight the cavalry?

130
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:26,600
Prince Bulei is dead.

131
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:27,560
What?

132
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,250
Princess Tuoya said

133
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:33,120
Lord Bai colluded with the grassland rebels to kill Prince Bulei.

134
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:34,919
I think she's talking nonsense.

135
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:37,559
How could my father possibly mix with rebels?

136
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:42,120
Imperial Father has ordered Lord Bai to be thrown into the Imperial Prison.

137
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,800
And that Shen Lingbo.

138
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,600
What about her?

139
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,640
She produced evidence claiming

140
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:51,100
the Song Army attempted to rebel.

141
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,320
Is that woman crazy?

142
00:08:53,720 --> 00:08:55,120
Things are tricky now.

143
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,280
People in court are agreeing,

144
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:59,080
and suspecting the Bai Army from back then as well.

145
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:01,780
Imperial Father ordered me to arrest Song Xuan.

146
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,280
We've been set up.

147
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,640
What do you mean?

148
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:08,000
There has been a huge conspiracy from the start.

149
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,240
The Bai family,

150
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,760
including Huanghuacai,

151
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,960
are all part of someone's scheme.

152
00:09:14,920 --> 00:09:16,600
Actually, I have that feeling too.

153
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:18,800
From Shen Lingbo turning on her family and writing to me,

154
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:21,330
to getting Lord Bai to chase Bulei's cavalry,

155
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:25,280
to Tuoya sending a message to lure Song Xuan away,

156
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:28,280
and finally Bulei's mysterious death.

157
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:31,960
All these events are just too suspicious.

158
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,800
But who is the mastermind?

159
00:09:34,280 --> 00:09:35,600
Shen Lingbo and Tuoya?

160
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,960
They have joined forces.

161
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,760
What is their goal in doing this?

162
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:42,640
Shen Lingbo is doing it for revenge.

163
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:44,540
If it were for revenge,

164
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:46,200
it should have ended

165
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,720
when Prime Minister Shen died.

166
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:50,050
Why is she disrupting the court like this?

167
00:09:50,280 --> 00:09:53,760
Shen Lingbo is a lunatic.

168
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:57,320
Maybe she really is a lunatic.

169
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,560
Third Prince,

170
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:04,960
you should stay here.

171
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,130
I have a feeling.

172
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,970
If you return to the palace,

173
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:11,000
Shen Lingbo and Tuoya will target you.
